{
  "uuid": "9665d79c0487f32a7d0aae07e65ec717",
  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Barista Supervisor",
  "description": "<p><strong>About the Role:</strong><br>\nJoin our team as a Barista Supervisor, where you'll bring our coffee and beverage experience to life! In this role, you'll prepare coffee and non-coffee beverages, handle cashiering and ordering, prepare simple hot food items, and deliver outstanding customer service to our guests.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Prepare coffee and non-coffee based beverages to the highest standard.</li>\n  <li>Assist with ordering, cashiering, and inventory management.</li>\n  <li>Prepare and serve a simple hot food menu.</li>\n  <li>Provide excellent customer service, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere for guests.</li>\n  <li>Assist and support coffee cart events when necessary</li>\n  <li>Oversee multiple sites, ensuring SOP and quality control.</li>\n  <li>Manage staff scheduling and training.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Working Hours:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>5-day work week</li>\n  <li>Office Hours</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>5-day work week</li>\n  <li>$1200 New Join Bonus (T&amp;C applies)</li>\n  <li>Staff discounts, birthday leave, medical benefits</li>\n  <li>Bi-annual bonus, skill development, and career progression</li>\n  <li>Training and uniform provided</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum 1 year of experience in a supervisory role in relevant industry.</li>\n  <li>Strong leadership, communication, and teamwork skills.</li>\n  <li>Ability to work in a fast-paced environment and handle multiple responsibilities.</li>\n  <li>Willing to travel to multiple locations</li>\n  <li>Basic barista skills with knowledge of coffee preparation techniques and equipment</li>\n  <li>Pleasant, positive attitude, responsible, and proactive</li>\n  <li>Strong interpersonal and communication skills</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you’re passionate about coffee and delivering great service, we’d love to hear from you! Apply today to join our team and start your coffee journey with us.</p>",
